{"tid":2196812,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有時諗諗下都係自己一個算","createTime":"2020-09-10T07:15:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-10T10:38:07.000Z","uid":185842,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bbdc6b55f834a6bea8dd175fc0784e121bfcfe8c","tid":2196812,"uid":185842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T07:15:59.000Z","msg":"本身諗住表白，但係句野去到喉嚨個陣，都講唔出，唔敢去開始一段新關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n諗諗下 自己都係想有時有個人可以陪下，其實普通朋友都得，又對搞野個啲無咩太大興趣，打個飛機都得，想搵個人分享大家嘅興趣，同屋企人又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係咪人越大，越難搵到一個啱自己，啱大家嘅，定係對拍拖睇透曬，無曬希望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唉 曾經都有個以為啱，但拍得越耐先知越唔啱，定係我變咗"},{"pid":"f58d29d61b5a09f85a80051bd5e06b9f1d4f351e","tid":2196812,"uid":185736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T07:31:20.000Z","msg":"緣份未到姐，唔好諗到咁灰～<br />\n順其自然啦～<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ee91e067e949a5768f57416b5f6704f3aea58bc","tid":2196812,"uid":9392,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f58d29d61b5a09f85a80051bd5e06b9f1d4f351e","tid":2196812,"uid":185736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T07:31:20.000Z","msg":"緣份未到姐，唔好諗到咁灰～<br />\n順其自然啦～<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T10:27:44.000Z","msg":"你鼓勵佢即係害死佢"},{"pid":"a87daf7cb9383bfa4b9fe071521dba94795fa62f","tid":2196812,"uid":373745,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T10:35:36.000Z","msg":"一個人不知幾撚fit 唔好比其他人既價值觀定型自己"},{"pid":"378448bb0adb32180ac71bb975a85b71ebe278e4","tid":2196812,"uid":368232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a87daf7cb9383bfa4b9fe071521dba94795fa62f","tid":2196812,"uid":373745,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T10:3